# Feature: sage repos — product atlas with sparklines.
Output ../assets/demo-repos.gif
Output build/demo-repos.txt
Set Width 1000
Set Height 500
Hide
Type "export PATH=$HOME/bin:$PATH NO_COLOR=1" Enter
Type "unset FORCE_COLOR 2>/dev/null; clear" Enter
Show
Type "sage repos"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 4s
